  <div class="tip" style="max-width:520px">
    <div class="tlbl">Security Debrief — What You Learned</div>
    ✦ <strong>Never share your Secret Recovery Phrase</strong> — not online, not by phone, not ever.<br>
    ✦ <strong>Only use support.ledger.com</strong> — real Ledger never DMs you first.<br>
    ✦ <strong>Verify every address character</strong> — address poisoning is nearly invisible.<br>
    ✦ <strong>Ignore unknown tokens</strong> — dusting maps your wallet identity.<br>
    ✦ <strong>Bookmark ledger.com</strong> — phishing lives in search ads and typosquat domains.
  </div>
  <div class="hv" style="font-size:24px;margin:10px 0 4px;text-shadow:0 0 15px var(--gold)" id="winScore"></div>
  <div class="hv" id="winRank" style="font-size:14px;color:#C41E1E;margin-bottom:14px"></div>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
    <button class="btn" onclick="restartGame(false)"><span>↺ PLAY AGAIN</span></button>
    <button class="btn" onclick="restartGame(true)"><span>⌂ TITLE SCREEN</span></button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PAUSE -->
<div class="scr off" id="sPAUSE">
  <div class="st" style="font-size:38px;margin-bottom:4px">⏸ PAUSED</div>
  <div class="ss" style="margin-bottom:16px">YOUR VAULT IS SAFE — FOR NOW</div>
  <div class="tip" style="max-width:380px;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:12px;line-height:1.9">
    <div class="tlbl">Controls</div>
    <strong style="color:var(--gold2)">WASD / Arrows</strong> — Move<br>
    <strong style="color:var(--gold2)">F</strong> — Toggle auto-fire / manual<br>
    <strong style="color:var(--gold2)">SPACE / Click</strong> — Fire (manual mode)<br>
    <strong style="color:var(--gold2)">E</strong> — Buy at shop<br>
    <strong style="color:var(--gold2)">ESC / P</strong> — Pause / Resume
  </div>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
    <button class="btn" onclick="resumeGame()"><span>▶ RESUME</span></button>
    <button class="btn" onclick="restartGame(true)"><span>⌂ TITLE SCREEN</span></button>
